text: isi taamat addunyay sissikuk taturta faxaah cagalah teetih taamitaah akeera nummayse waa numuh nanu fannah nanim teetil (Addunya kinnuk) kaah naceeh naysissike, keenik nanu ninnih kah naysissikem fanna numuh, tohuk lakal akeeral jahannam gira dabqi kaak abnaah usuk bura luk Yallih Racmatak axxaaruk tet cula
